25	FAULCONBRIDGE	Son to Sir Robert Faulconbridge. (ROBERT:)
26	
27	PHILIP the BASTARD	his half-brother. (BASTARD:)
28	
29	JAMES GURNEY	servant to Lady Faulconbridge. (GURNEY:)
30	
31	PETER Of Pomfret	a prophet. (PETER:)
32	
33	PHILIP	King of France. (KING PHILIP:)
34	
