36	
37	LYMOGES	Duke of AUSTRIA. (AUSTRIA:)
38	
39	CARDINAL PANDULPH	the Pope's legate.
40	
41	MELUN	a French Lord.
42	
43	CHATILLON	ambassador from France to King John.
44	
45	QUEEN ELINOR	mother to King John.
46	
