48	
49	BLANCH of Spain	niece to King John. (BLANCH:)
50	
51	LADY FAULCONBRIDGE:
52	
53	Lords, Citizens of Angiers, Sheriff, Heralds,
54	Officers, Soldiers, Messengers, and other Attendants.
55	(First Citizen:)
